    "title": "Mid-Level Fleet Manager at DSV India",
    "description": "DSV India invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Fleet Manager at our Delhi location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout DSV India:\nDSV India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in 3PL Management\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in KPI Monitoring\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Delhi, Delhi, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with DSV India!",
